data.description: The one you've been waiting for! Home features a formal living and dining room, beautiful kitchen with eat in area, as well as a huge living room. Enjoy evenings or morning coffee in the morning room right off the kitchen. Enjoy movies or game night in the huge third floor loft.  Need an office or craft room this home has a designated space on the first floor.  Four bedrooms located on the second floor including the primary, and fifth bedroom with full bathroom on the third floor.  Large 2 car attached garage with plenty of parking.
